    <h1>Become a Member</h1>
    
    <p>The Rust Foundation is a 501(c)6 non-profit organization incorporated in Delaware, USA. The primary way to participate in this organization is to become a member.</p>
    
    <p>Membership benefits include representation on the Board of Directors. Check out our overview deck to learn more.</p>
    
    <div class="cta-gradient button"><a href="/static/rust-foundation-overview.pdf">Membership Overview Deck</a></div>

